VVibrant vocals
p3
sVnews
p4
VR.K. Srikantan enthralledrasikaswith his vocal prowess at a concert in Vylloppilly Samskriti Bhavan, Thiruvananthapuram. The octogenarian gave a memorable three-and-a-half hour concert.He started with the Ada tala varnam &#8216;Viriboni&#8217; in Bhairavi. He continued  with &#8216;Sidhivinayakam anisham&#8217; in Shanmukhapriya set to Roopaka tala. Tyagaraja&#8217;s &#8216;Nada thanu manisam&#8217; in Chithamani (Adi) was noted for its rich bhava. &#8216;Manasa Bhajare Bhaja Manasam&#8217; in Kanada (Chappu talam) was bhakti laden.After a short raga alaap, Srikantan rendered Tyagaraja&#8217;s &#8216;Paluka vemi&#8217; in Poornachandrika set to Adi tala. After a neat delineation of Kamas, the vocalist presented &#8216;Sujana jeevana Rama,&#8217; which was set to Roopaka tala. The Tyagaraja composition was noted for its vibrant presentation.However, the attraction of the evening was the Tyagaraja kriti &#8216;Bhavanutha&#8217; in Mohanam.Yet another captivating piece was a ragam tanam pallavi (Kalyani) set to Khanda jati triputa talam. After an elaborate exposition of the raga, he rendered the &#8216;tanam num thak thaka thaka num tha.&#8217; The violin  complemented the vocalist. The pallavi was &#8216;Eashako danda kandana durina janaka Rama.&#8217;The thaniavarthanam that followed saw deft strokes on the mridangam by Umayalpuram Sivaraman and on the ghatam by Thripunithura Radhakrishnan.Srikantan was given vocal support by his son Ramakanth.Srikantan also rendered &#8216;Vachamago charame&#8217; in Kaikavashi, &#8216;Smara manasa Padbhanabham&#8217; (Darbar), &#8216;Varanarada&#8217; (Vijayasree), &#8216;Bhogeendra sayinam&#8217; (Kundalavarali), &#8216;Ksheerasagara sayana&#8217; (Devagandhari), &#8216;Eswari Rajeswari&#8217; (Abheri), &#8216;Smariso sarvada&#8217; (Hamir kalyani), a thillana (Jenjutti) and mangalam.A memorable concert, it was marked with vitality, stress on sahitya, laya, tonal quality and above all adherence to classicism. &#8216;Swathi 08&#8217; was organised by Swaralaya and Srikantan&#8217;s concert was the inaugural concert.Srikantan and Umayalpuram Sivaraman were honoured at the function.
